    private static final String AvailableCommand = "Now there are 3 ways to add a Tasks.Task to list (Replace your <task> with your task name:
	1.todo <task>
	2.deadline <task> by <MM-dd hh:mm am/pm or MM-dd> (where mm is minute and MM is month)
	3.event <task>
		3.1event <task> <mm:hh am/pm> to <mm:hh am/pm> 
		3.2event <task> <MM/dd> <mm:hh am/pm> to <mm:hh am/pm>";

    private static final String AvailableListOperation = "Here is what you can do with the tasks once added to the list:
	 1.mark (to make a mark on the task) <the number of task on the list>
	 2.unmark (to unmark a task on the list) <the number of task on the list>
	 3.remove (to remove a task from the list) <the number of task on the list>
	 4.list (to show the current list)";
